In [ ]:
plt.figure(figsize=(12,5))
drop_outlier_col = Price
for idx, i in enumerate(drop_outlier_col):
    Q1 = Price[i].quantile(0.25)
    Q3 = Price[i].quantile(0.75)
    IQR = Q3 - Q1
    lower_bound = Q1 - 1.5 * IQR
    upper_bound = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR
    Price = Price[(Price[i] >= lower_bound) & (Price[i] <= upper_bound)]
    sns.boxplot(x=i, data=Price)
    plt.title(i, backgroundcolor='black', color='white', fontsize=15)
    plt.xlabel(i, size=12)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

def adf_test(Price):
  result=adfuller(Price)
  labels=['adf_test','p_values',' tr',' quan sat']
  for value,label in zip(result,labels):
    print(label + ' : ' +str(value))
  if result[1]<=0.05:
    print('u iu kin bac bo H0 d liu co tinh dng (Chp nhn H0)')
  else:
    print('Cha u iu kin bac bo H0 d liu khng co tinh dng (Chp nhn H1)')
adf_test(Price)

adf_test : -2.087730145865558
p_values : 0.2494769077873089
 tr : 2
 quan sat : 1031
Cha u iu kin bac bo H0 d liu khng co tinh dng (Chp nhn H1)

xy dng c ARIMA model thi chui thi gian cua chung ta phai la chui dng vi m hinh ARIMA se gia inh chui thi gian cua ta a dng nn ta se dung phng phap kim ra la ADF

ADF la mt phng phap kim tra xem trong chui thi gian cua chung ta co nut gc hay khng. Chung ta se co cp gia thuyt bao gm:

  • H0: co 1 nut gc, chui cha dng
  • H1: khng co nut gc, chui a dng

Trong trng hp nay:

  • Gi tr thng k kim nh ADF (ADF Test Statistic) l -2.087730145865558. Khi gi tr ny l mt s m, ngha l chui c xu hng hi t v trng thi cn bng di hn sau khi loi b cc yu t tm thi v nghim n v.
  • Vi gi tr p l 0.2494769077873089, ln hn mc ngha thng k alpha thng thng l 0.05. iu ny ng rng khng bng chng bc b gi thuyt H, tc l chui khng c tnh dng.

=> Do , da vo kt qu kim nh ADF, chng ta khng c bng chng kt lun rng chui khng c tnh dng. iu ny ng rng chng ta cn phi thc hin thm cc bin php bin i chui thnh chui c tnh dng trc khi tin hnh m hnh ha hoc d bo.

adf_test : -22.43629689926186
p_values : 0.0
 tr : 1
 quan sat : 1031
u iu kin bac bo H0 d liu co tinh dng (Chp nhn H0)

Kt qu kim nh Augmented Dickey-Fuller (ADF) cho thy:

  • Gi tr thng k kim nh ADF (ADF Test Statistic) l -29.511822495505015.
  • Gi tr p (p-value) rt nh, gn vi 0.0, nh hn mc ngha thng k thng thng l 0.05. iu ny cho thy c bng chng bc b gi thuyt H, ng rng d liu c tnh dng.
  • Do gi tr p rt nh, chng ta c th kt lun rng d liu c tnh dng sau khi sai phn bc 1. iu ny lm cho chui thi gian ph hp p dng cc m hnh v phng php d bo c yu cu v tnh dng nh ARIMA. =>d=1

import pmdarima as pm
def arima(timeseries):
  automodel=pm.auto_arima(timeseries,
                          start_p=0,
                          start_q=0,
                          d=1,
                          max_p=8,
                          max_q=8,
                          test='adf',
                          seasonal=False,
                          trace=True)
  return automodel

So snh cc ch s:

Mean Absolute Error (MAE):

MAE o lng ln trung bnh ca cc sai s d on. M hnh 1 c MAE = 2448.45, trong khi M hnh 2 c MAE = 211.72. MAE ca M hnh 2 thp hn rt nhiu so vi M hnh 1, cho thy M hnh 2 c cc d on gn vi gi tr thc t hn.

Mean Squared Error (MSE):

MSE o lng bnh phng trung bnh ca cc sai s d on, lm ni bt cc sai s ln hn.

M hnh 1 c MSE = 8241643.98, trong khi M hnh 2 c MSE = 109835.03. MSE ca M hnh 2 thp hn rt nhiu so vi M hnh 1, cho thy M hnh 2 c hiu sut tt hn, c bit l trong vic gim cc sai s ln.

Root Mean Squared Error (RMSE):

RMSE l cn bc hai ca MSE v cng o lng ln trung bnh ca cc sai s d on. M hnh 1 c RMSE = 2870.83, trong khi M hnh 2 c RMSE = 331.41. RMSE ca M hnh 2 thp hn rt nhiu so vi M hnh 1, cho thy M hnh 2 c cc d on chnh xc hn.

Mean Absolute Percentage Error (MAPE):

MAPE o lng ln trung bnh ca cc sai s d on di dng phn trm. Tuy nhin, c hai m hnh u c gi tr MAPE l nan (not a number), c th do cc gi tr thc t ca chui thi gian c gi tr bng khng hoc rt nh, dn n php tnh phn trm b li.

Kt lun:

Da trn cc ch s MAE, MSE v RMSE, M hnh 2 r rng c hiu sut tt hn nhiu so vi M hnh 1. Cc sai s d on ca M hnh 2 nh hn rt nhiu so vi M hnh 1, cho thy M hnh 2 c kh nng d on chnh xc hn. Ch s MAPE khng cung cp thng tin hu ch trong trng hp ny do gi tr nan.
